{"tid":437431,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國報紙頭版驚見「中國強國崛起」六字","createTime":"2017-10-16T04:00:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-17T04:16:55.000Z","uid":37554,"like":235,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"c9de5f8fb7bb30bcb309e642d5be50d183b03368","tid":437431,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T04:00:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DMMRKM2XkAAg1YV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDMMRKM2XkAAg1YV.jpg&h=27c67fb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCCTV報導<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vwr3qa4d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvwr3qa4d&h=4aa1c218&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n環球網<br />\n10月15日，在法國《世界報》的法文頭版報導中出現了六個醒目的中文大字：中國，強國崛起。當天，《世界報》一期報紙用了八個版面的篇幅專門講述&ldquo;中國，強國崛起&rdquo;的故事，這樣的做法實屬罕見<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.weibo.com/ttarticle/p/show?id=2309351000144163252476096385\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weibo.com%2Fttarticle%2Fp%2Fshow%3Fid%3D2309351000144163252476096385&d=Om5fu%2FRzhLHckwMXTPZrkC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=34b661cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.weibo.com/ttarticle/p/show?id=2309351000144163252476096385</a><br />\n<br />\n懂法文的網友留言提示說&ldquo;這是諷刺中國的文章&rdquo;，這些媒體才刪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有懂法文的網友翻譯了八個版面的內容 分別是中國政府準備加大集權封建力度，全面控制人民及企業。權利切割下的經濟，人民及企業未來的生活及獲利會更加緊縮壓迫；黨權膨脹；私人軍隊；自由民主離中國越來越遠。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DMMRKMzX4AAdR7E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDMMRKMzX4AAdR7E.jpg&h=ce93dcea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36c94888a4174a1c1603eb93d7711d6950601242","tid":437431,"uid":18912,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T04:01:37.000Z","msg":"😂"},{"pid":"a9b8a421527f4fb10930018362b25302334e7891","tid":437431,"uid":49392,"like":106,"dislike":1,"score":105,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T04:02:13.000Z","msg":"見到強國呢兩個字都要估下係唔係曲線"},{